<br>
Is skill increase related to hits, or related to swings?<br>
<br>
If it is related to hits, /disc Precise should help.  If it is only related to swings, then that disc won't make any difference.<br>
<br>
Of course, a lower delay weapon will increase both swings and hits, so that helps.<br>
<br>
