Offense and weapons skill increases are based on two things, and that is your DEX and numbers of swings taken. <br>
<br>
Defensive skills are based on your AGI and number of swings you have recieved. <br>
<br>
I suggest getting your DEX and AGI up to at least 100 (120 is better) to increase your skill level everytime you ding, also switch to the fastest weapon you can get your hands on, regardless of damage output. <br>
<br>
Once your skills are maxed for that level, the go ahead and switch back to +AC equipment and you regular weapon. <br>
<br>
If you want to see for yourself how much these stats do make a difference, make a barby warrior mule with various stats and play with each one for half an hour or so. You'll see for yourself just how much difference it makes when you put the max amount of skill points into DEX or AGI. <br>
<br>
